{"tid":913394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［本地獨立出版］保家不必衛國 - 香港民間軍事化簡論 1669 -1899","createTime":"2018-11-23T11:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T11:14:09.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"269daf1562c17a5f73c554a93e6940f601d7e9ef","tid":913394,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T11:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UegynTm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUegynTm.png&h=ea8c0859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本社即將出版的 #保家不必衛國，主要講述清朝時候香港地區的軍事化過程，當中包括海盜、圍村、政府兵力等文件檔案。作者除了對之有一番嚴肅的分析探討之外，本書更有大量圖表，部分更是作者與家人親自拍攝，可見其用功的態度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/23/190904_f6065c3867f442452b92312c55e7a763.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F23%2F190904_f6065c3867f442452b92312c55e7a763.png&h=bf908c76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/23/190908_6349cac94d0778231c162d65ba2b0843.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F23%2F190908_6349cac94d0778231c162d65ba2b0843.png&h=984e1f5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/23/190913_a05e92e94b6597a1ad37c90f1f43fea5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F23%2F190913_a05e92e94b6597a1ad37c90f1f43fea5.png&h=5281de64&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/23/190917_a3db362361a4a01dbeb393b7a6475be8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F23%2F190917_a3db362361a4a01dbeb393b7a6475be8.png&h=84323a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/23/190923_dca9fd25f1c95b934e1fa7a68f103d40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fup